Achievements.Name: The New Apprentice
Achievements.Description: Started your apprenticeship with some help from your humble guide, Percy.

Achievements.Name: Recording Artist
Achievements.Description: Recorded your own unique music in a Hot Spot for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Haberdashing
Achievements.Description: Earned the right to wear "The Hat."

Achievements.Name: Musical Score
Achievements.Description: Completed a Score Goal and revealed a remix.

Achievements.Name: Spelling It Out
Achievements.Description: Discovered your first Composition Spell in a realm.

Achievements.Name: Chromatic Variations
Achievements.Description: Discovered all 5 Composition Spells in realms.

Achievements.Name: School Reunion
Achievements.Description: Reunited the Master Sorcerer with his former apprentice.

Achievements.Name: In Too Deep
Achievements.Description: Used the Composition Spell in the Shadows.

Achievements.Name: Safe Haven
Achievements.Description: Used the Composition Spell in the Haven.

Achievements.Name: City Slicker
Achievements.Description: Used the Composition Spell in the Neighborhood.

Achievements.Name: Seed Planted
Achievements.Description: Used the Composition Spell in the Plant.

Achievements.Name: Musica Universalis
Achievements.Description: Used the Composition Spell in the Cosmos.

Achievements.Name: Record Collector
Achievements.Description: Created a recording in every Hot Spot in the realms.

Achievements.Name: Magic Touch
Achievements.Description: Discovered all of the Magic Fragments in the realms.

Achievements.Name: Page Turner
Achievements.Description: Viewed a journal page while exploring a realm.

Achievements.Name: Journalist
Achievements.Description: Collected all of the journal pages.

Achievements.Name: Librarian
Achievements.Description: Played a song in the Song Library.

Achievements.Name: Off the Record
Achievements.Description: Viewed a recording of a saved performance.

Achievements.Name: Switch Hitter
Achievements.Description: Switched to a new mix 150 times.

Achievements.Name: Purist
Achievements.Description: Played 3 songs with all mixes available, but only used a single mix.

Achievements.Name: All Mixed Up
Achievements.Description: Played an entire song with audio components from all 3 mixes present at all times.

Achievements.Name: Multifaceted
Achievements.Description: Hit every cue on 40 different Composition Spells in songs.

Achievements.Name: Edged Out
Achievements.Description: Refrained from opening a Composition Spell by missing a single side.

Achievements.Name: Careful Composer
Achievements.Description: Spent 120 seconds working on a recording in a Composition Spell.

Achievements.Name: In the Mix
Achievements.Description: Revealed every available mix for 15 songs.

Achievements.Name: Mix Master
Achievements.Description: Revealed every available mix for all 33 on-disc songs.

Achievements.Name: Virtuoso
Achievements.Description: Earned Five Golden Notes on a song in Single Player mode.

Achievements.Name: Noteworthy
Achievements.Description: Earned Five Golden Notes on 5 songs in Single Player mode.

Achievements.Name: Goal Oriented
Achievements.Description: Completed every available goal for 15 songs.

Achievements.Name: Goal Star
Achievements.Description: Completed every available goal for all on-disc songs.

Achievements.Name: Dueling Duet
Achievements.Description: Completed a song in Multiplayer Mode.

Achievements.Name: Take Five
Achievements.Description: Created recordings with all 5 Composition Spells in Multiplayer Mode.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Harmony
Achievements.Description: Earned Five Golden Notes as a team on a song in Multiplayer Mode.

Achievements.Name: Multi-instrumentalist
Achievements.Description: Made music with 7 different instruments in a single visit to The Workshop.

Achievements.Name: Broom Mate
Achievements.Description: Bought the celebrated broom to life in The Workshop.

Achievements.Name: Feeling Crabby
Achievements.Description: Coaxed a shy performer out of his shell in The Shoal.

Achievements.Name: Creative Spark
Achievements.Description: Put on an electifying performance with all of the jellyfish in The Shadows.

Achievements.Name: Falling Starfish
Achievements.Description: Juggled starfish for 30 seconds in The Shadows.

Achievements.Name: Fairy Weather Friend
Achievements.Description: Led the fairies to 4 different secret spots in The Hollow.

Achievements.Name: Hidden Talent
Achievements.Description: Found Mischief, the sneaky yeti, in all of his hiding spots in The Haven.

Achievements.Name: Nine Lives
Achievements.Description: Played 9 different musical variations with the kittens in The Haven.

Achievements.Name: Flame War
Achievements.Description: Deflected the dragon's fire 50 times in The Nation.

Achievements.Name: Steaks on a Train
Achievements.Description: Created a recording with both of the "food groups" in a single visit to The Neighborhood.

Achievements.Name: Room and Board
Achievements.Description: Found new homes for the elephant and the fish in The Neighborhood.

Achievements.Name: Locomotion Picture
Achievements.Description: Stamped graffiti onto the train in The Neighborhood.

Achievements.Name: Equal Opportunity Employer
Achievements.Description: Had a workforce that included Fix-Bots of both sizes and all 3 colors in The Press.

Achievements.Name: Paper Menagerie
Achievements.Description: Played a continuous 25-note melody using all 3 types of paper creatures in The Plant.

Achievements.Name: Circuit Bender
Achievements.Description: Kept all 4 rows of The Motherboard lit in The Plant for 10 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Creature Comfort
Achievements.Description: Showed 7 different movie clips to the lonely astronaut in The Capsule.

Achievements.Name: Dark Side of the Moons
Achievements.Description: Spun all 3 of the moons in The Cosmos.
